description: Revised application for demolition of existing commercial building and erection of 177 self-contained dwellings (including 85 units of affordable housing), comprising 28 four-bedroom town houses, 19 three-bedroom town houses, 11 one-bedroom flats 111 two-bedroom flats and 8 three-bedroom flats and 141 car-parking spaces, 1,500m of public open space, and associated landscaping and servicing
